Kita berusaha membantu Tang San.

102
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:03,760
Sudah lama tak ada
yang bisa memaksaku.

103
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,590
Nyalakan Cincin Roh ketiga!

104
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,110
Hati-hati!

105
00:13:26,470 --> 00:13:27,790
Ou Sike, Ning Ronrong,
turunlah!

106
00:13:28,640 --> 00:13:29,400
Kami masih bisa.

107
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,080
Kalau tidak, akan mati!

108
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:32,710
Kalian turun dulu.

109
00:13:37,230 --> 00:13:37,670
Ayo.

110
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,440
Ayo.

