00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,520
Kupotong tanganmu.

112
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:53,960
Tulang Roh?

113
00:13:54,590 --> 00:13:55,840
Banyak juga caramu.

114
00:14:34,230 --> 00:14:35,150
Sampai di sini saja.

115
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,520
Siapa yang bisa menahan
belati bulanku?

116
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:27,910
Takutnya kehidupan Tang San
tak akan tenang lagi.

117
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,840
Roh Pelindung Ganda,
Palu Hao Tian?

118
00:15:36,350 --> 00:15:37,960
Kau juga termasuk berbakat.

119
00:15:39,030 --> 00:15:42,200
