00:17:50,850 --> 00:17:54,230
Upacara pemberian hadiah dimulai,
Leluhur Pertama dipersilakan.

142
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:57,190
Tunggu sebentar.

143
00:19:01,180 --> 00:19:02,290
Bagaimana kau bisa tahu?

144
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:05,640
Meski kau bersembunyi dalam
dimensi Roh Pelindung,…

145
00:19:06,350 --> 00:19:07,640
